  "content": "<p data-pid=\"yZYgw99d\">看起来没有人推荐 Anki 啊，我来介绍一下好了，我是从高二下开始用这个 app 的，主要用它来记笔记和复习。</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b019693f3e2c57021b13aa522406dfa7_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"711\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-original-token=\"v2-b019693f3e2c57021b13aa522406dfa7\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"711\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b019693f3e2c57021b13aa522406dfa7_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;711&#39; height=&#39;1920&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"711\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-original-token=\"v2-b019693f3e2c57021b13aa522406dfa7\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"711\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b019693f3e2c57021b13aa522406dfa7_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b019693f3e2c57021b13aa522406dfa7_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"GuMT448B\">一句话介绍：我们把笔记以卡片的形式记在 Anki 上，Anki 会按照算法安排复习时机，长期使用可以记住自己所学知识的 90% 以上而不会忘记。</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e4fd11cd9f56271482314e33e6c47218_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1365\" data-rawheight=\"741\" data-original-token=\"v2-1097e9f4ac166a27aa53dcaa93e21abc\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e790e6a76ba526d433f4016974a4ac77_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1365\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e4fd11cd9f56271482314e33e6c47218_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1365&#39; height=&#39;741&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1365\" data-rawheight=\"741\" data-original-token=\"v2-1097e9f4ac166a27aa53dcaa93e21abc\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e790e6a76ba526d433f4016974a4ac77_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1365\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e4fd11cd9f56271482314e33e6c47218_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e4fd11cd9f56271482314e33e6c47218_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"ydvfLyLs\">Anki 是怎么做到的呢？两个关键词：间隔重复、测试效应。</p><p data-pid=\"ojOB0XNd\"><b>间隔重复</b>，就是将我们学习过的知识，按照熟悉程度来安排下次复习的日期。Anki 的算法能让大部分知识在我们快要忘掉它们的时候出现在我们面前，提高我们的复习效率，不把时间<b>浪费</b>在复习<b>熟知</b>的知识和<b>重新</b>学习<b>忘记</b>的知识上面。</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-50b26f6aa6ad245ee3e844d04dc1442e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1207\" data-rawheight=\"679\" data-original-token=\"v2-50b26f6aa6ad245ee3e844d04dc1442e\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1207\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-50b26f6aa6ad245ee3e844d04dc1442e_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1207&#39; height=&#39;679&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1207\" data-rawheight=\"679\" data-original-token=\"v2-50b26f6aa6ad245ee3e844d04dc1442e\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1207\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-50b26f6aa6ad245ee3e844d04dc1442e_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-50b26f6aa6ad245ee3e844d04dc1442e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"Vsu8A_x8\"><b>测试效应</b>，则是通过看问题、想答案的复习方法，激发我们复习的<b>主动性</b>，从而提高我们复习的效果。研究表明，通过这种测试形式的复习，能够提高<b>长期记忆</b>效果 13% ！</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7423c891616807705fd539588ea1e2de_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1210\" data-rawheight=\"679\" data-original-token=\"v2-7423c891616807705fd539588ea1e2de\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1210\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7423c891616807705fd539588ea1e2de_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1210&#39; height=&#39;679&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1210\" data-rawheight=\"679\" data-original-token=\"v2-7423c891616807705fd539588ea1e2de\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1210\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7423c891616807705fd539588ea1e2de_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7423c891616807705fd539588ea1e2de_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"7Vkg8Gnd\">让我们看看 Anki 里是什么样的：</p><p data-pid=\"Nc3BN9fX\">间隔重复：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a61ac293b80f8b3803dd3122c9d6ad8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"366\" data-original-token=\"v2-4a61ac293b80f8b3803dd3122c9d6ad8\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4a61ac293b80f8b3803dd3122c9d6ad8_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;366&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"366\" data-original-token=\"v2-4a61ac293b80f8b3803dd3122c9d6ad8\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4a61ac293b80f8b3803dd3122c9d6ad8_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a61ac293b80f8b3803dd3122c9d6ad8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"x-toDv2Y\">测试效应：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-20d50031f4fd3464e19584f9c68ab210_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"634\" data-rawheight=\"542\" data-original-token=\"v2-20d50031f4fd3464e19584f9c68ab210\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"634\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-20d50031f4fd3464e19584f9c68ab210_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;634&#39; height=&#39;542&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"634\" data-rawheight=\"542\" data-original-token=\"v2-20d50031f4fd3464e19584f9c68ab210\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"634\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-20d50031f4fd3464e19584f9c68ab210_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-20d50031f4fd3464e19584f9c68ab210_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"VWihJuOF\">不仅如此，Anki 的适用性很广，我高中的时候用它来记英语、语文、生物、化学，还有一些数学常用值和物理常识：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8277c8d53c6e0419fc320a97c19a777f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"908\" data-rawheight=\"549\" data-original-token=\"v2-ec953bf9bc7154c4ede106181c22d855\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4b1d46043088664e5ec97a1b37144230_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"908\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8277c8d53c6e0419fc320a97c19a777f_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;908&#39; height=&#39;549&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"908\" data-rawheight=\"549\" data-original-token=\"v2-ec953bf9bc7154c4ede106181c22d855\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4b1d46043088664e5ec97a1b37144230_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"908\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8277c8d53c6e0419fc320a97c19a777f_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8277c8d53c6e0419fc320a97c19a777f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-503410525cbb1d0b2c644473b5603fe6_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2188\" data-original-token=\"v2-e024b77618139e0d826efcd396f24f26\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c4849c97a51c7b153aea06d07305b5a3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-503410525cbb1d0b2c644473b5603fe6_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;2188&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2188\" data-original-token=\"v2-e024b77618139e0d826efcd396f24f26\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c4849c97a51c7b153aea06d07305b5a3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-503410525cbb1d0b2c644473b5603fe6_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-503410525cbb1d0b2c644473b5603fe6_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-90bdc27ee1cf0971c7f290ecf0c220d6_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1272\" data-rawheight=\"766\" data-original-token=\"v2-bc420849ed6eda7554ab8e4160af89c9\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-94496898c0c3388f507948c42d428d28_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1272\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-90bdc27ee1cf0971c7f290ecf0c220d6_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1272&#39; height=&#39;766&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1272\" data-rawheight=\"766\" data-original-token=\"v2-bc420849ed6eda7554ab8e4160af89c9\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-94496898c0c3388f507948c42d428d28_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1272\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-90bdc27ee1cf0971c7f290ecf0c220d6_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-90bdc27ee1cf0971c7f290ecf0c220d6_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><hr/><p data-pid=\"1Ybryzm3\">Anki 支持 windows、mac、linux、安卓、苹果等常见设备，并且可以多端同步，走到哪学到哪。</p><p data-pid=\"PWAbUOL-\">为了帮到有缘人，我写了一份快速上手教程：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/61564332\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2e8a109841199b0a18e70ae7bd16ea66_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1220\" data-image-height=\"535\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：B 站 Ankidroid 视频教程与电子书(全平台教程)快速通道</a>",
